Expectedly, the announcement of the death of former Chief of Staff, Abba Kyari to President Muhammadu Buhari generated a lot reactions from diverse people in the social media space. In the early hours of Saturday morning, personalities took to their tweeter handles to pour out their tributes to the Presidency and family of the late Chief of Staff. Mallam Abba Kyari, tested positive to COVID-19 and had since been receiving treatment till he passed on. Three of his staff reportedly tested positive too.   